Package de.patricklammers.vorlesungsplan.app.actionbar

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionBarHelper
    An abstract class that handles some common action bar-related functionality in the app.
    ActionBarHelperBase
    A class that implements the action bar pattern for pre-Honeycomb devices.
    ActionBarHelperHoneycomb
    An extension of ActionBarHelper that provides Android 3.0-specific functionality for Honeycomb tablets.
    ActionBarHelperICS
    An extension of de.dhbw.mosbach.app.actionbar.example.android.actionbarcompat.ActionBarHelper that provides Android 4.0-specific functionality for IceCreamSandwich devices.
    SimpleMenu
    A really dumb implementation of the Menu interface, that's only useful for our actionbar-compat purposes.
    SimpleMenuItem
    A really dumb implementation of the MenuItem interface, that's only useful for our actionbar-compat purposes.
